== not a search for foundations of our knowledge == 

It is tempting, at this point, to suggest that the principles of reasoning are
bedrock. That no further justification is required. But what we are seeking is
not justification. No more than an account of the physical processes of the eye
increase confidence in our vision.  But rather we want an account of how
physical creatures such as ourselves can be sensitive to such justifications.


